    "description": "Narayana Health Digital invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Senior Software Engineer at our Jabalpur location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Narayana Health Digital:\nNarayana Health Digital is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Flexible working hours\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Narayana Health Digital!",
